# Terraform AWS 3-Tier (VPC + ALB + ASG) ðŸš€

Production-style **dev/stage/prod** environments using Terraform:
- VPC with public/private subnets + NAT
- Application Load Balancer
- Auto Scaling Group (EC2) with Nginx user_data
- Security groups (least privilege)
- Outputs the ALB DNS

> RDS module is planned as a v2 upgrade.

## Architecture (Mermaid)
```mermaid
flowchart TB
  subgraph VPC
    direction LR
    subgraph Public Subnets
      ALB[ALB]
    end
    subgraph Private Subnets
      EC2A[EC2 in ASG] --- TG[Target Group] --> ALB
      EC2B[EC2 in ASG]
    end
  end
  Internet((Internet)) --> ALB
